1
00:00:07,460 --> 00:00:10,180
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,180 --> 00:00:14,140
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:16,820
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:19,820
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:24,700
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:25,660 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:29,260 --> 00:00:30,820
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:34,660
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:39,340
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:43,660
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,140 --> 00:00:50,060
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:50,620 --> 00:00:54,220
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:57,940
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:58,900 --> 00:01:04,900
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:11,700
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:16,660
=Episode 23=
(This story is entirely fictional.)

17
00:01:16,950 --> 00:01:17,550
What was I supposed to do?

18
00:01:17,750 --> 00:01:18,630
Follow

19
00:01:18,630 --> 00:01:19,790
a conscienceless scumbag like you

20
00:01:19,790 --> 00:01:20,950
and starve?

21
00:01:20,950 --> 00:01:21,430
You...

22
00:01:22,850 --> 00:01:23,760
Marquis of Zhennan,

23
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,990
right now,

24
00:01:25,150 --> 00:01:26,390
your household's granaries

25
00:01:26,390 --> 00:01:28,230
are already bursting
with overpriced grain.

26
00:01:28,270 --> 00:01:30,030
I'm afraid your entire household

27
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:31,230
can't even scrape together

28
00:01:31,230 --> 00:01:32,390
a single coin.

29
00:01:33,350 --> 00:01:34,150
Marquis of Zhennan,

30
00:01:34,870 --> 00:01:36,070
don't fall for his cunning trap.

31
00:01:36,270 --> 00:01:37,390
Let's unite against the common enemy.

32
00:01:37,390 --> 00:01:38,990
Family matters can be dealt with later.

33
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,150
Li Yunhe,

34
00:01:41,950 --> 00:01:42,910
you've got some clever tricks

35
00:01:42,910 --> 00:01:44,150
up your sleeve.

36
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:45,630
But do you really think

37
00:01:45,630 --> 00:01:46,670
you can turn the tide

38
00:01:46,670 --> 00:01:47,990
against all odds

39
00:01:47,990 --> 00:01:49,190
with just this handful of men?

40
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:51,030
Count us in too!

41
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,110
Greetings, Your Majesty.

42
00:02:07,390 --> 00:02:09,190
I'm Sun Yunshang, commander
of the Dragon Guard.

43
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:10,590
Rise, Ms. Sun.

44
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:11,510
Thank you, Your Majesty.

45
00:02:18,390 --> 00:02:20,150
This person's former identity

46
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,310
was the manager of Chunfeng Pavilion.

47
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:23,510
She's the one who sheltered Xue Bingxiu.

48
00:02:24,990 --> 00:02:25,950
You tricked me?

49
00:02:26,110 --> 00:02:28,110
How else do you think Xue Bingxiu

50
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:29,990
ended up here in Feng City?

51
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:32,070
Oh, my dear uncle,

52
00:02:32,670 --> 00:02:35,590
how could you take a bait that obvious?

53
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,270
What?

54
00:02:38,570 --> 00:02:40,610
So they had this planned
from the very beginning?

55
00:02:40,890 --> 00:02:41,970
What's there to panic about?

56
00:02:42,490 --> 00:02:44,130
How many men
does the Dragon Guard even have?

57
00:02:44,410 --> 00:02:45,170
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk)
You have over ten thousand men

58
00:02:45,290 --> 00:02:46,490
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk)
under your command.

59
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:47,690
The upper hand is still ours.

60
00:02:48,790 --> 00:02:50,310
And what if you add us to the mix?

61
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:02,270
Yu.

62
00:03:04,390 --> 00:03:05,590
Who are all these people?

63
00:03:05,990 --> 00:03:06,910
Prince Ning,

64
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:08,390
now,

65
00:03:08,790 --> 00:03:10,590
do you still have the upper hand?

66
00:03:11,630 --> 00:03:12,670
And us too!

67
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,870
And who the hell are you?

68
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:19,590
I'm the head of the Xie family.

69
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:21,070
Guys, show them what we've got!

70
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:22,270
Yeah!

71
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:24,790
You insolent peasants...

72
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:26,710
Are you trying to start a rebellion?

73
00:03:26,830 --> 00:03:29,110
Get the hell back to
whatever hole you crawled out of!

74
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:30,590
Or else,

75
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:33,590
I'll have all your clans exterminated!

76
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:38,910
Good people of Feng City,

77
00:03:39,110 --> 00:03:41,110
we're acting under imperial orders

78
00:03:41,110 --> 00:03:42,790
to apprehend rebels.

79
00:03:42,830 --> 00:03:43,230
Please,

80
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:44,110
don't be deceived

81
00:03:44,110 --> 00:03:45,670
by their wicked lies and delusions,

82
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:46,790
lest you end up

83
00:03:46,790 --> 00:03:48,670
with your entire family beheaded.

84
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:50,190
You'll only regret it!

85
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:56,590
Fellow townsfolk,

86
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,550
you'd better hold onto

87
00:03:58,950 --> 00:04:00,790
those weapons in your hands
nice and tight.

88
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,670
Once you drop your weapons,

89
00:04:02,670 --> 00:04:04,630
I'm not sure whether your clans
get wiped out,

90
00:04:04,830 --> 00:04:05,830
but you yourselves

91
00:04:06,270 --> 00:04:07,790
will be the first to suffer.

92
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,390
Mr. Li,

93
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,390
the Marquis of Zhennan
says he's arresting rebels,

94
00:04:11,390 --> 00:04:13,230
but the Zhou family says
the Marquis is the rebel.

95
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:14,630
What in the world is going on here?

96
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:16,470
Let me ask you one thing.

97
00:04:17,230 --> 00:04:18,710
Do you trust me,

98
00:04:19,110 --> 00:04:20,830
or do you trust the Marquis of Zhennan?

99
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:22,270
We trust you!

100
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:23,550
- We trust you!
- We trust you!

101
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:25,390
If it weren't for Mr. Li

102
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,990
using his wisdom and clever strategies,

103
00:04:26,990 --> 00:04:28,510
the Marquis House would have long

104
00:04:28,510 --> 00:04:29,790
since starved us all,

105
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:30,910
left to die of hunger!

106
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:31,590
That's right!

107
00:04:31,710 --> 00:04:32,830
It was Li Yunhe

108
00:04:33,030 --> 00:04:34,270
who saved everyone!

109
00:04:34,390 --> 00:04:36,390
Mr. Li, we trust you!

110
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,430
- We trust you!
- We trust you!

111
00:04:37,670 --> 00:04:38,590
- We trust you!
- We trust Li Yunhe!

112
00:04:38,910 --> 00:04:40,390
You filthy peasants!

113
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,790
So you really are rebelling!

114
00:04:42,230 --> 00:04:43,190
Marquis of Zhennan,

115
00:04:43,910 --> 00:04:45,270
don't tell me you actually believed

116
00:04:45,270 --> 00:04:46,270
Feng City

117
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:49,390
belongs to your Marquis House?

118
00:04:49,470 --> 00:04:52,110
Feng City belongs to its people.

119
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,790
Prince Ning, Marquis of Zhennan,

120
00:04:55,230 --> 00:04:56,470
you want to stage a rebellion?

121
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:57,790
First, you'd better ask
the people of Feng City

122
00:04:57,790 --> 00:04:59,390
whether they agree to it.

123
00:04:59,790 --> 00:05:00,430
Fellow townsfolk,

124
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:02,110
do you agree?

125
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:04,310
- No!
- We don't!

126
00:05:04,310 --> 00:05:05,310
- No!
- We don't!

127
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:07,390
We'll fight these corrupt officials

128
00:05:07,590 --> 00:05:10,470
and treacherous rebels
to the bitter end!

129
00:05:10,870 --> 00:05:11,910
Just a pack of filthy lowlifes

130
00:05:12,590 --> 00:05:14,030
dares to stand in the way
of my grand ambition?

131
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:15,510
Dream on!

132
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:16,630
Soldiers! Kill them all!

133
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:17,670
Leave no one standing!

134
00:05:18,510 --> 00:05:19,310
Hold it right there!

135
00:05:20,590 --> 00:05:21,830
Soldiers,

136
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:23,590
guys,

137
00:05:23,710 --> 00:05:25,470
you're the ones garrisoning Feng City.

138
00:05:25,470 --> 00:05:27,870
Think back to when you couldn't
even afford grain.

139
00:05:27,910 --> 00:05:28,750
Who was it

140
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,390
that forced the grain prices down

141
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,270
so you could have food in your bellies?

142
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:38,870
The sovereign feeds you,

143
00:05:38,990 --> 00:05:40,430
then you should know a subject's duty.

144
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:42,390
His Majesty stands here before you.

145
00:05:42,790 --> 00:05:45,070
If you follow Prince Ning
and the Marquis of Zhennan in rebellion,

146
00:05:45,670 --> 00:05:47,790
even if you win, you may not get fed.

147
00:05:47,790 --> 00:05:48,470
But if you lose,

148
00:05:48,990 --> 00:05:51,270
your clans really will be wiped out.

149
00:05:52,230 --> 00:05:52,990
Soldiers,

150
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:55,190
hundreds of thousands
of Feng City's people

151
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:57,070
all stand behind His Majesty.

152
00:05:57,670 --> 00:05:59,790
Do you want to stick to rebellion
to its very end

153
00:06:00,030 --> 00:06:01,350
or pledge yourselves to His Majesty

154
00:06:01,670 --> 00:06:03,070
and root out these traitors?

155
00:06:04,030 --> 00:06:05,390
Think very carefully.

156
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:06,950
I'll pay the back pay

157
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:09,310
that Prince Ning and the Marquis
of Zhennan can't deliver.

158
00:06:09,990 --> 00:06:10,990
I'll also offer the opportunities

159
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:13,390
that Prince Ning
and the Marquis of Zhennan can't offer.

160
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:14,870
I have

161
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,030
plenty of money

162
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:17,430
and grain,

163
00:06:18,030 --> 00:06:19,830
which is more than enough
to keep you all fed.

164
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:22,710
The man who captures Prince Ning

165
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:24,710
shall be rewarded
with 10,000 taels of gold.

166
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:33,870
The one who captures Prince Ning
and the Marquis of Zhennan alive

167
00:06:34,110 --> 00:06:35,630
shall be promoted in rank and title,

168
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:37,310
with blessings
extending to their family!

169
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:38,190
Attack now!

170
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:38,830
Charge!

171
00:06:41,990 --> 00:06:42,790
You...

172
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,670
Capture the Marquis of Zhennan alive!

173
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,590
Sworn warriors of the Marquis House!

174
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:48,830
Protect my father!

175
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:49,590
Understood!

176
00:06:53,670 --> 00:06:54,830
Protect His Majesty.

177
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:57,790
Guys! For Feng City,

178
00:06:57,910 --> 00:06:58,710
charge!

179
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:13,630
Ladies!

180
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:15,310
Charge!

181
00:07:26,590 --> 00:07:27,390
Guys!

182
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:28,910
Kill them all!

183
00:07:51,190 --> 00:07:51,990
My dear uncle,

184
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:53,990
with things as they stand,

185
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:55,830
do you have any last words?

186
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:59,310
I thought
that with you traveling incognito,

187
00:07:59,590 --> 00:08:01,110
newly arrived in Feng City,

188
00:08:01,110 --> 00:08:02,190
your roots would not yet run deep,

189
00:08:03,030 --> 00:08:04,070
that those childish tricks of yours

190
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:05,830
stood no chance against me.

191
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:07,990
Oh, but what a pity...

192
00:08:08,230 --> 00:08:10,150
It's a pity
that for all your meticulous plotting,

193
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:11,910
you forgot to factor him in.

194
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:13,190
Yunhe,

195
00:08:13,590 --> 00:08:14,870
you've rendered meritorious service.

196
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:16,590
Your Majesty flatters me.

197
00:08:16,990 --> 00:08:18,790
This was all thanks to Your Majesty's
overwhelming good fortune,

198
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:21,070
plus Prince Ning's underestimation
of his opponent.

199
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:22,150
Otherwise,

200
00:08:22,350 --> 00:08:23,230
we would never

201
00:08:23,230 --> 00:08:24,430
have won so easily.

202
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:25,630
Yes,

203
00:08:26,350 --> 00:08:27,830
I did underestimate you.

204
00:08:28,230 --> 00:08:29,110
If only

205
00:08:29,670 --> 00:08:31,910
you could have served under me...

206
00:08:31,910 --> 00:08:33,190
Even now,

207
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:34,630
you still don't understand
the true reason

208
00:08:35,190 --> 00:08:36,630
for your defeat.

209
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:38,390
You couldn't see people
for what they truly were.

210
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:41,190
Look at them.

211
00:08:42,070 --> 00:08:44,110
Do they look like men who could
ever accomplish anything great?

212
00:08:44,310 --> 00:08:46,230
Li Yunhe,
I'll never let you get away with this!

213
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:46,710
Kneel!

214
00:08:47,150 --> 00:08:47,670
Stay down!

215
00:08:48,590 --> 00:08:49,790
Plotting rebellion is a crime

216
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:51,990
punishable
by the entire clan's extermination.

217
00:08:52,230 --> 00:08:53,710
You'll never let me get away with this?

218
00:08:54,110 --> 00:08:55,990
Better save that for your next life.

219
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:58,430
Still running your mouth
in the face of death?

220
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:00,470
Throw them all into the Imperial Prison

221
00:09:00,470 --> 00:09:01,630
to await their execution.

222
00:09:01,710 --> 00:09:02,190
Understood.

223
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:03,830
Hold on.

224
00:09:05,430 --> 00:09:06,110
Yunzhuo,

225
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:07,350
could you

226
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:09,510
have Lu Qifeng castrated first

227
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:10,590
and let me take him back to the palace?

228
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:12,110
Your Highness!

229
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:12,910
Father!

230
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:14,120
Your Highness!

231
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:15,790
Granted.

232
00:09:15,990 --> 00:09:16,350
Father!

233
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:17,350
Your Majesty!

234
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:18,390
- Father!
- Your Majesty!

235
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:19,510
Your Majesty!

236
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:20,270
Your Majesty!

237
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:20,990
Father!

238
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:21,630
Your Majesty!

239
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,110
Father, save me!

240
00:09:22,190 --> 00:09:22,790
Your Majesty!

241
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:24,590
Father, save me!

242
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:36,710
For failing to recognize
Your Majesty and Her Highness,

243
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:38,390
and for my many prior offenses,

244
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,030
I beg Your Majesty's forgiveness.

245
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:43,110
Li Yunhe,

246
00:09:43,110 --> 00:09:44,790
you call that many prior offenses?

247
00:09:44,990 --> 00:09:46,350
You practically
worked the emperor and me

248
00:09:46,350 --> 00:09:47,710
like beasts of burden.

249
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:49,590
I'm absolutely going

250
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:51,470
to settle the scores with you.

251
00:09:52,310 --> 00:09:53,190
Your Highness,

252
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:54,830
back then, I simply

253
00:09:55,190 --> 00:09:56,790
had no idea you were a princess.

254
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:59,790
Yunzhuo, you absolutely

255
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:01,630
cannot let him off lightly this time.

256
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,510
How about

257
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:05,830
we have him castrated too,
and bring him back to the palace?

258
00:10:07,390 --> 00:10:07,910
What...

259
00:10:07,990 --> 00:10:08,710
Your Majesty,

260
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:10,270
you can't listen to her!

261
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:12,190
You just ordered
to have Lu Qifeng castrated!

262
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:13,070
That's enough.

263
00:10:13,190 --> 00:10:13,990
You may rise.

264
00:10:14,710 --> 00:10:15,590
Thank you, Your Majesty.

265
00:10:16,590 --> 00:10:18,630
Li Yunhe, for your meritorious service,

266
00:10:18,630 --> 00:10:19,790
what reward do you desire?

267
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:22,390
As long as I can grant it,

268
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:23,390
I shall certainly agree.

269
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:25,870
I want...

270
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:28,190
Your Majesty, let Li Yunhe

271
00:10:28,190 --> 00:10:29,870
serve as the magistrate of Feng City.

272
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:31,030
That's right.

273
00:10:31,190 --> 00:10:32,190
If Mr. Li

274
00:10:32,190 --> 00:10:33,710
could stay in Feng City as an official,

275
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:35,270
it would truly
be Feng City's great fortune,

276
00:10:35,310 --> 00:10:36,710
a blessing for all its people!

277
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:38,190
What are you all thinking?

278
00:10:38,310 --> 00:10:39,910
Mr. Li has incredible knowledge

279
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:40,990
and peerless talent.

280
00:10:40,990 --> 00:10:42,990
He's destined for the imperial cabinet.

281
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:45,430
Since the Marquis of Zhennan
has been kicked to the curb,

282
00:10:45,590 --> 00:10:47,110
why not just let Mr. Li

283
00:10:47,110 --> 00:10:48,390
be the new Marquis of Zhennan?

284
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:49,230
Exactly.

285
00:10:49,430 --> 00:10:51,390
Let Mr. Li be the Marquis of Zhennan

286
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:53,190
and lead Feng City to go big, go strong,

287
00:10:53,190 --> 00:10:54,070
and reach new heights of glory.

288
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:58,790
Li Yunhe, have you made up your mind?

289
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:00,430
Your learning is profound,

290
00:11:00,430 --> 00:11:01,910
and you deeply grasp
the art of governance.

291
00:11:02,590 --> 00:11:03,830
If you are willing,

292
00:11:03,990 --> 00:11:05,270
I shall notify the Ministry of Personnel

293
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:07,670
to grant you a fitting official post.

294
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:10,590
Your Majesty, I...

295
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:13,190
I don't wish to be an official.

296
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:14,230
I understand.

297
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:16,110
Then what is it that you want?

298
00:11:17,190 --> 00:11:18,310
I'm not

299
00:11:18,310 --> 00:11:20,190
a greedy man.

300
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:21,550
How about

301
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:23,750
you simply reward me with

302
00:11:24,070 --> 00:11:25,310
a few hundred thousand taels of gold

303
00:11:25,470 --> 00:11:26,790
just as a token gesture?

304
00:11:27,190 --> 00:11:28,590
You actually have
the nerve to ask for that.

305
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:30,510
You're the sovereign
of the mighty Daqian.

306
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:31,910
Every word you speak
carries great weight.

307
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:33,310
Surely you can't

308
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:35,110
go back on your own word?

309
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:36,590
Can't you ask

310
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:37,630
for something proper?

311
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:38,710
I don't really

312
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:40,790
have anything I want.

313
00:11:46,390 --> 00:11:48,190
Well, I don't have that much.

314
00:11:48,590 --> 00:11:49,790
But as for beauties,

315
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,110
I happen to know one.

316
00:11:52,790 --> 00:11:55,270
As it happens, Ziyao
is yet to be betrothed.

317
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:57,270
You shall be her prince consort.

318
00:11:57,590 --> 00:11:58,870
Uh, no, thanks.

319
00:11:59,030 --> 00:11:59,910
No?

320
00:12:00,590 --> 00:12:02,790
What's that supposed to mean, Li Yunhe?

321
00:12:03,070 --> 00:12:05,070
Are you saying I'm too ugly for you?

322
00:12:05,070 --> 00:12:07,230
No, that's not what I meant at all.

323
00:12:07,910 --> 00:12:08,790
Your Highness,

324
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:10,590
what I mean is, I...

325
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:11,390
I...

326
00:12:15,470 --> 00:12:17,030
Your Highness, have you forgotten?

327
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:19,230
I'm still the Zhou live-in son-in-law.

328
00:12:19,310 --> 00:12:21,030
Weren't you already divorced?

329
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:22,790
You're no longer
a live-in son-in-law now.

330
00:12:22,870 --> 00:12:24,270
With all due respect, you may not know

331
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:25,110
that Yu hasn't signed

332
00:12:25,110 --> 00:12:26,590
the divorce letter yet.

333
00:12:26,590 --> 00:12:28,390
So it doesn't count.

334
00:12:30,710 --> 00:12:31,590
You might want to

335
00:12:31,950 --> 00:12:33,110
take a look at this.

336
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:35,390
I...

337
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:41,300
(Divorce Letter)

338
00:12:42,990 --> 00:12:44,590
Yu, you...

339
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:45,710
Li Yunhe,

340
00:12:46,390 --> 00:12:47,150
you've now achieved

341
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:48,910
fame and success

342
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:50,070
and even gained

343
00:12:50,270 --> 00:12:52,870
the favor of His Majesty
and Her Highness.

344
00:12:53,310 --> 00:12:56,790
Our marriage contract
should come to an end.

345
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:00,590
Yu,

346
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:02,630
did they force you?

347
00:13:02,870 --> 00:13:04,670
Rest assured, with me here,

348
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:05,830
no one dares bully you.

349
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:07,190
No one forced me.

350
00:13:07,270 --> 00:13:08,470
It was my own choice.

351
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:09,870
Our marriage contract

352
00:13:10,070 --> 00:13:10,790
was always about avoiding

353
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,710
the forced marriage
from the Marquis House.

354
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:13,990
It was just a farce.

355
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:14,910
And now,

356
00:13:14,910 --> 00:13:17,310
this farce should
finally come to an end.

357
00:13:17,790 --> 00:13:19,830
Li Yunhe, did you hear that?

358
00:13:19,830 --> 00:13:21,470
Yu has already divorced you.

359
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:22,790
And I'm willing

360
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:24,190
to let bygones be bygones.

361
00:13:24,270 --> 00:13:25,430
Just go

362
00:13:25,430 --> 00:13:26,790
to the palace with me

363
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:28,190
and be my prince consort.

364
00:13:30,230 --> 00:13:31,030
Zhou Xingyu,

365
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:32,990
you really know how to put me in a spot.

366
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:45,990
What divorce letter,

367
00:13:46,310 --> 00:13:47,230
Your Highness?

368
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:48,630
You must be mistaken.

369
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,470
There's no divorce letter.

370
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:50,630
That doesn't exist.

371
00:13:53,590 --> 00:13:55,790
Zhou Xingyu,
listen to me loud and clear.

372
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:57,310
I swear

373
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:59,230
to the heavens,

374
00:13:59,470 --> 00:14:01,790
in this life,
I shall marry none but you.

375
00:14:02,590 --> 00:14:03,270
Li Yunhe...

376
00:14:03,270 --> 00:14:04,070
What now?

377
00:14:05,590 --> 00:14:06,510
I'm still

378
00:14:06,510 --> 00:14:07,590
the Zhou live-in son-in-law.

379
00:14:07,870 --> 00:14:08,470
Didn't you think

380
00:14:08,470 --> 00:14:10,390
getting divorced
was a blessing back then?

381
00:14:10,590 --> 00:14:12,390
It's not that he didn't want
to be a live-in son-in-law.

382
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:14,270
He wanted to prove himself.

383
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:15,790
As expected of my sworn brother,

384
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:16,670
you know me.

385
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:17,910
You truly

386
00:14:18,350 --> 00:14:19,910
don't want to divorce me?

387
00:14:20,510 --> 00:14:21,310
You'd even

388
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,510
throw away the chance to be

389
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:24,870
the prince consort of Daqian?

390
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,990
In this life, in my heart,

391
00:14:28,190 --> 00:14:29,590
there's only room enough

392
00:14:29,990 --> 00:14:32,190
for you alone, Zhou Xiaoyu.

393
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:33,670
Your Highness,

394
00:14:34,430 --> 00:14:35,510
I'm truly sorry.

395
00:14:36,390 --> 00:14:37,190
I'm still

396
00:14:37,190 --> 00:14:39,110
the Zhou live-in son-in-law.

397
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:41,070
I can't be your prince consort.

398
00:14:41,390 --> 00:14:42,870
Humph. Li Yunhe,

399
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:44,190
who even wants you anyway?

400
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,070
I won't waste my time on you anymore.

401
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:48,150
Escort me back to the capital!

402
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:49,790
Yunhe, until we meet again.

403
00:14:55,670 --> 00:14:56,870
They've left.

